{"id":310192,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-薄案开庭维权人士申请旁听遭诬陷，济南/","date":"2013-08-23T09:04:04Z","modified":"2013-08-23T09:04:04Z","title":"维权网 | 薄案开庭维权人士申请旁听遭诬陷，济南警方上演闹剧（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日下午，河北鲍润蒲，天津郑建慧、张文艳、郑光泉，山东林秀丽等人一起到山东省济南市中级法院，按照法院规定办理了旁听手续，一行五人感到出乎预料的顺利，同时也希望通过旁听见证中国司法是否公正。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>不料，当他们离开济南市中级法院，前行五、六十米的路口时，突然闖出一个身穿蓝色衣服的男子，拽住张文艳的背包就喊：“别走！你偷了我的钱包”。鲍润蒲、郑光泉等人上去讲理。蓝衣男子声称有证人，又拽住了鲍润蒲的背包，一口咬定是鲍润蒲偷了钱包，并说是在某某饭店里偷的钱包，有录像，还报了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>济南警方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>赶到现场，蓝衣男子以命令的口气说：“把他们带派出所去”。济南警察不问青红皂白就要大家的身份证，并说：“你们是嫌疑人去派出所”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>鲍润蒲据理力争，要求：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、警方拿出传唤证否则绝对不会去派出所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、既然污蔑我们是嫌疑人，要履行告知义务，报案人姓氏名谁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、谁主张谁举证，证人到现场，拿出录像。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>郑建慧要求：警方现场办公，蓝衣人说出钱包的形状、颜色及钱包内的东西，我们当场打开各自背包，现场的中外记者及济南市民是见证人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张文艳坚持：拿不出证据，损坏了我们的名誉当众给我们赔礼道歉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现场有济南市民围观，大家对此议论纷纷：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>济南市民甲：蓝衣人是警察今天没穿制服。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>乙：维稳，上午抓走不少外地人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>丙：旁听，这不是送上门来了吗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>丁：有老外不好抓人……</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>事情僵持近一个小时，济南警方无法带走五位维权访民，最后以去饭店取录像为由就一去不复返了。济南警方和蓝衣人在薄案开庭前上演的一</span><span>场污蔑闹剧</span><span>，在众多济南市民的围观和数十名中外记者的关注下收场。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-2-l68sZ09s8/Uhbj4NnRf_I/AAAAAAAAnMs/88U1qRznUrQ/s1600/2013-08-21+16.17.30.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-2-l68sZ09s8/Uhbj4NnRf_I/AAAAAAAAnMs/88U1qRznUrQ/s320/2013-08-21+16.17.30.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9SY21LOM--I/Uhbj1xJptfI/AAAAAAAAnMk/ySmBIb1wBBo/s1600/2013-08-21+15.43.42.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9SY21LOM--I/Uhbj1xJptfI/AAAAAAAAnMk/ySmBIb1wBBo/s320/2013-08-21+15.43.42.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q5S4FJgscys/Uhbj2BRPUVI/AAAAAAAAnMg/Kc5Zvx9LhmQ/s1600/2013-08-21+06.08.52.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q5S4FJgscys/Uhbj2BRPUVI/AAAAAAAAnMg/Kc5Zvx9LhmQ/s320/2013-08-21+06.08.52.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}